casebody.data:
Sally Langner et al. v. Jessup Holding, Inc., et al. Jessup Holding, Inc., v. Maintenance Company, Inc.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, with 010 costs, unless appellants, Jessup Holding, Inc., and Maintenance Company, Inc., procure the record on appeal and appellants’ points to be served and filed on or before August 11, 1959, with notice of argument for the September 1959 Term of this court, said appeals to he argued or submitted when reached. Concur — Botein, P. J., Rabin, Valente, McNally and Stevens, JJ.
